        "TileImage": "$($repository 799e5b66-b968-4ecf-b2f5-a99a892138fe).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\r\rJournalist Ruby Red isn’t just observing the bank — she’s attempting to take control of it. Her network is already in place, quietly working toward that goal.\r\rOne guard, complete with an impressive mustache, seems more interested in Ruby than his actual duties. She doesn’t appear to mind the attention either. A questionable distraction, at best.\r\rDisrupt her operation, 47. And try not to get caught up in the… personal dynamics.\r\rGood Luck 47.\r-Twiice",
